Project 1: Sales Forecasting with Linear Regression
Problem Statement:
Businesses struggle to estimate future sales based on past
performance.
Objective:
Build a regression model to predict future sales using historical
data.
Requirements:
Use a CSV file with sales data (date, product, quantity, revenue)
Preprocess data, handle null values
Apply Linear Regression
Plot actual vs predicted sales
Expected Outcome:
Graphical and tabular forecasts for upcoming sales periods.
